        "System.Description": "VCS Branch: zeus-1_0_2-1912<hr>Request from Camie Lafaver(Bank OPS)\n<br><br>We would like to pull the \u201cShort Name\u201d from Aviva based on the account number and have it show in the \u201cCustomer Name\u201d field on the Teller side(currently titled Identification on virtual ticket) and add a description field for the teller to make notes that the customer needs to see on the virtual tickets.\n<br><br>1- Pull Aviva Short name into Customer Name field in all DDA and SAV transactions and lock the field\n<br><div>2- Add a &quot;Tran Description&quot; field to DDA and SAV transactions.&nbsp;<br></div><br><br>Additional details attached\n<br><hr>Reporter: Mohammed Mohiuddin<hr>External ID: 1912<hr>Components: <hr>Affiliates affected: NBA,NSB,VBC,ZFNB,ABT,CBT<hr>Original assignee: Zeus Configuration Management<hr>Found with a Test Case",
